                "accept_rate": 75
            },
            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 3.0",
            "score": 2,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1410282312,
            "creation_date": 1410282312,
            "body": "<p>There is 1402 characters which are considered lower case.<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>int count = 0;\nfor(char ch = Character.MIN_VALUE; ch &lt; Character.MAX_VALUE;ch++)\n    if (Character.isLowerCase(ch))\n        count++;\nSystem.out.println(\"Lower case is \" + count);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
